title: S3 EP8: Gus Walks Into a Bank
description:
This week, Maggie & Tim talk about Season 3 Episode 8, the one where Gus gets taken hostage in a bank and Shawn has to become the lead negotiator to save his best friend. Plus, Juliet has a new romantic interest and it's not who you think it is.
